**Sine:**\ $\sin 0 = 0$; rises to $1$ at $\frac{\pi}{2}$; 
 returns to $0$ at $\pi$; dips to $-1$ at $\frac{3\pi}{2}$; 
 completes the cycle at $2\pi$. Domain: $(-\infty,\infty)$. 
 Range: $[-1,1]$.

**Cosine:**\ $\cos 0 = 1$; falls to $0$ at $\frac{\pi}{2}$; 
 reaches $-1$ at $\pi$; returns to $0$ at $\frac{3\pi}{2}$; 
 completes the cycle at $2\pi$. Domain: $(-\infty,\infty)$. 
 Range: $[-1,1]$.
